<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Jesus is my life</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 CHORUS
 All the world should know
 That Jesus is my life (x3)

[V2]
 Sometimes it's hard to carry on
 Sometimes you're
 in the middle of the noise
 And you feel down

[V3]
 While I found the only King
 The only God
 From the sky
 From my heart I sing:

[V4]
 CHORUS
 All the world should know
 That Jesus is my life (x3)

[V5]
 Don't you know there's
 Someone who can turn
 Your sadness into a joyful song
 And you can try

[V6]
 Lay down your burden at the cross
 The Bible tells you won't be lost
 You're in the right way

[V7]
 CHORUS
 All the world should know
 That Jesus is my life (x3)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1695</hymn_number>
<author>Marco Prezioso</author>
</song>